        おはよう！
      .chat-main__message-main__message-box__message-info
        .chat-main__message-main__message-box__message-info__message-name
          sama
        .chat-main__message-main__message-box__message-info__message-date
          2019/11/20(wed) 17:50:01
      .chat-main__message-main__message-box__message-detail
        今起きたの！？
  .chat-main__message-form
    = form_for [@group, @message] do |f|
      = f.text_field :content, class: 'chat-main__message-form__text', placeholder: 'type a message'
      .chat-main__message-form__mask
        = f.label :image, class: 'chat-main__message-form__mask__image' do
          = icon('fas', 'image', class: 'chat-main__message-form__mask__image__icon')
          = f.file_field :image, class: 'chat-main__message-form__mask__image__hidden'
      = f.submit 'Send', class: 'chat-main__message-form__submit'